metadata.name: Theory Of Extension
metadata.description: It may have been said, that if the ones that were truly loved at a time, all together, lifted their hands to stretch them up into the sky, only them, if they believed that they were able to fly, only then, and if they could detach their fingers pointing to the moon, only there, they could have seen that they were already been hovering over the ground, ready to head up to that time they were truly loved and extend it to infinity
